    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The observational registry provides 214 CPB cases spanning all five target operating points, and CFD RH predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at every operating point. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
